Subject: Busses & Balloons

The Albuquerque Air Alliance and Route 66 Splits present the 8th Annual 
Busses and Balloons Show and Shine!

Dates: Friday Oct. 1st thru Sunday Oct. 3rd

Location: New Covenant Church Parking Lot. The street address is 7201 Paseo 
Del Norte, ABQ, NM 87113. For a map, click here.

Times: Registration opens on Friday at Noon. All vehicles must be off of the 
show site by 9:00 a.m. Sunday morning.

Cost: Show spots $10 Camping Spots $10 Swap Spots $10 Venders $20

General Public Admission: $2 or 2 canned goods for Road Runner Food Bank

Lunch: As always, Foreign Aide will be providing a free lunch on Saturday 
afternoon!

Who's Welcome: ALL types of Volkswagens are welcome and encouraged to 
participate in the show. Bugs, Ghia's, Sandrails, Things, etc. If it's an 
air-ccoled VW - it's welocme!

Site Policies: Dogs are not allowed on the show grounds, but can be camped 
with off the pavement if restrained. NO ferocious dogs at all. No on ground 
campfires, but BBQ's and other off-ground firepits OK.

Show Prizes: The Judging this year will be done by all registered show 
participants. There will simply be a top twenty that encompasses all types 
of VW's. It's basically a people's choice deal this year.

Show Raffle: Raffle tickets will be available for a small fee. All proceeds 
form the raffle go to benefit Road Runner Food Bank


Here is a printable copy of the flyer. Just right click on either of the
links below - select "save as", choose your destination, and BAMMO! you now 
have
the flyer on your computer. Open it up and print away!

